</li><li> <a class="urllink" href="http://www.nndb.com/people/995/000024923/hank-williams-jr-3-sized.jpg">And<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a><small>&loz;</small>, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/HankWilliamsJr" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/HankWilliamsJr">Hank Williams Jr.</a> , who gets extra Badass points for having grown it to cover up facial scars that resulted from him falling off a mountain.
</li></ul></li><li> Commander, Murphy, the 'late' Demon Barber, and the Keymaster of <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/TheProtomen" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/TheProtomen">The Protomen</a>. The band <a class="urllink" href="http://www.protomen.com/BeardsGoingNowhere/">even wrote a song about beards<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>.
