</li><li> The Briscoes. The plate Jay chose for the "real" <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Wrestling/RingOfHonor" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Wrestling/RingOfHonor">ROH</a> world title belt was a bearded skull.
</li><li> The Marquee Bruce Santee is instantly recognizable thanks to his goatee.
</li><li> Travis "Tyson" Tomko, whose beard, tattoos, bald head, and black ring attire make him look like a total badass. <a class="urllink" href="http://www.powerprowrestlingfigs.com/images/uploads/TysonTomko.jpg">[3]<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a><small>&loz;</small>
</li><li> Sensacional Carlitos has a pretty short beard but makes up for it by shaving <a class="urllink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vc-NyX2z5Dg">designs into it<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>.(since he's in the link you could also count Mr 450)
