</li><li> Your IWA Texas ACW <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TagTeam" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TagTeam">Tag Team</a> Champions, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Wrestling/LondonAndKendrick" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Wrestling/LondonAndKendrick">Paul London</a>, Jack Jameson, Two Dudes With Facial Pubes!
