</li></ul></li><li> Jack Cayman of <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MadWorld" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/MadWorld">MadWorld</a></em>. It helps that he looks a lot like <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/CowboyBebop" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/CowboyBebop">Jet Black</a>.
